review.heading: Great series
review.content: Totally enjoyable series and so many twists on storyline. Awesome cinematography, screenplay and acting. I personally love the role of "Khaanzyada". This series deserves more than 7 stars. Those people who are doing negative review without watching it please do watch it.

review.heading: Enjoyable
review.content: Just watched this movie, It was a funny/kind of horror movie. Dialogues followed current trends. I love Arjun Kapoor's acting since ki & ka, here also he did an amazing job. You can watch it, you will surely enjoy it.

review.heading: Complex but mind blowing content
review.content: Wow, so much loops.. Bold acting, awesome cinematography. Worth watching.And Raima Sen was looking fabulous.
